<a href="/wiki/Eugene_Wigner" title="Eugene Wigner">Eugene Wigner</a><sup id="cite_ref-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-1"><span class="cite_crochet">[</span>1<span class="cite_crochet">]</span></a></sup></td>
